OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain will
OL,6,Fspread northeast from mid-evening.
OL,7,FThis clearing through the early hours
OL,8,Fallowing drier weather to follow,
OL,9,Fbecoming mostly dry by morning. Fresh
OL,10,Fto strong southwesterly winds
OL,11,Fdeveloping across the far northwest.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FWindy with rain at times
OL,14,Facross the west, this turning more
OL,15,Fpersistent later. Dry in the east with
OL,16,Fsome brightness along the Moray coast.
OL,17,FMild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
