OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fand mild with rain on Wednesday, drier
OL,7,Fwith a few showers later. Bright and
OL,8,Fbreezy with showers on Thursday.
OL,9,FChance of rain Friday, especially
OL,10,Facross the south, otherwise showers.
